flowchart TD
    A[User highlights text on webpage] --> B[User clicks browser extension icon]
    B --> C[Extension popup opens]
    C --> D[User clicks 'Verify' button]
    D --> E[Extension sends text to backend API via fetch]
    E --> F[Backend receives request in app.py]
    F --> G[Backend preprocesses text]
    G --> H[Backend runs inference on selected model]
    H --> I[Model returns prediction: Fake or Real]
    I --> J[Backend sends response back to extension]
    J --> K[Extension displays result in popup]
    K --> L[User sees 'Fake' or 'Real' verdict]